            <h2>International Journal of Remote Sensing, 2013</h2>
            <img src="images/papers-3.jpg" />

            <div class="table">
              <p><b>To cite this article:</b> G.C. Stove, J. McManus, M.J. Robinson, G.D.C. Stove & A. Odell (2013): Ground penetrating abilities of a new coherent radio wave and microwave imaging spectrometer, International Journal of Remote Sensing, 34:1, 303-324
              <b>To link to this article:</b> <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1080/01431161.2012.713529">http://dx.doi.org/10.1080/01431161.2012.713529</a></p>
